<aura:documentation>
	<aura:description>
    <div class="slds-m-top_large">
    <h4>Overview</h4>
    <p>The <code>&lt;c:PEG_ActivityDisplay_CMP&gt;</code> component is a pure data display
        UX component. When instantiating the component, all the data required should be 
        provided via its <code>activity</code> attribute (as a JSON object).</p>
    <p>Custom actions may also be configured via two other attributes providing the
        list of actions and a callback invoked in the containing component.</p>
<pre>&lt;c:PEG_ActivityDisplay_CMP
    activity="{!eachItem}"
    actionMenu="{!v.rowActionJson}"
    menuCallback="{!c.handleRowAction}"/&gt;</pre>
    <br/>
    </div>
    
